        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Harbor for Terror Act</strong></p> <p>This bill repeals authority granted to the President to except Iran's energy, shipping, and shipbuilding sectors from sanctions in order to provide for reconstruction assistance or economic development in Afghanistan.</p>]]>
        </text>
